deps.context:
find_package(
    qt5 config required
    components core
               network
               test
               widgets)

libs.content:
find_library(
  diasdk_lib
  names diaguids.lib
  path_suffixes "lib/"
  hints "$env{vsinstalldir}/dia sdk" "${cmake_generator_instance}/dia sdk")

find_program(
  diasdk_dll msdia140.dll
  path_suffixes "bin/"
  hints "$env{vsinstalldir}/dia sdk" "${cmake_generator_instance}/dia sdk")
